drawings.author: ZWZhNTMzZTE2NzI3
drawings.text: These are here as potential audience members if there is an ongoing case in the courtroom.

drawings.author: ZWZhNTMzZTE2NzI3
drawings.text: The carriage requires 2 horses to move. Unless otherwise stated, the horses are not automatically present, however are placed to the side for your convenience.

drawings.author: ZWZhNTMzZTE2NzI3
drawings.text: When court is in session, the magister and his guard are in the courtroom. When not, he is in his office.
